{"tid":1514951,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信查元朗鄉黑套丁 你我有責(懶人包)","createTime":"2019-08-29T03:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T03:31:44.000Z","uid":194452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"023f254f6ef7bf78be0317c743dbbc7057be7236","tid":1514951,"uid":194452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:05:30.000Z","msg":"除左主線, 得閒就做下支線, 只需幾分鐘, 得閒就打個電話問下進度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YPmOiP0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYPmOiP0.png&h=81d40214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTo:        landsd@landsd.gov.hk <br />\nCc:        prosrdu3@doj.gov.hk<br />\nSubject:        要求地政總署調查套丁個案 <br />\n<br />\n敬啟者<br />\n本人為香港市民，現要求地政總署積極調查下列案件，若有疑點須即時轉交執法部門跟進處理。<br />\n<br />\n本人翻查判詞，發現以下案件已經在各級法院審結一段日子，案情均顯示男丁與發展商之間簽署秘密協議發展套丁屋苑。在男丁申請丁屋前簽署秘密協議，則有可能在協議雙方執行協議內容時，令分區地政處誤信申請丁屋的男丁在村內建屋自住，但實質上男丁在發展商指使下，隱瞞出賣丁權予發展商的意圖，涉嫌觸犯作虛假陳述，或在宣誓下作假證供的罪名。以上案情皆被法庭接納為事實，然而未見執法部門採取果斷行動。<br />\n<br />\n政府的消極行為已向涉嫌違法者釋出錯誤訊息，以致多年來違法套丁情況日益猖獗，令「鄉黑」勢力坐大，亦令市民對政府施政失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n為挽回市民對法治的信心，本人嚴正要求地政總署立刻展開積極調查：<br />\n<br />\n案件編號 (地點)：<br />\nHCA 2741/1998 （元朗 蓮花地）(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/31U3g4b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31U3g4b&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=1354cd9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/31U3g4b</a>)<br />\nHCA 729/2011 （元朗八鄉水盞田村）(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KXxoF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KXxoF4&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=71142f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KXxoF4</a>)<br />\nHCA 16693/1999 （元朗蓮花地 錦福豪園）(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/33Kr6kT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33Kr6kT&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=e42eb129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/33Kr6kT</a>)<br />\nHCA 2251/2002 （元朗流浮山輞井圍）(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2HfW1fc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HfW1fc&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=7a2bd839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2HfW1fc</a>)<br />\nHCA 2500/2013 （元朗八鄉水盞田村）(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NiwKow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NiwKow&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=bf0fc5fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2NiwKow</a>)<br />\nDCCJ 2780/2014 （元朗深涌村）(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NliOdi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NliOdi&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=031fe4f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2NliOdi</a>)<br />\nDCCJ 1286/2008 （元朗錦田元崗村）(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2MqWHTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MqWHTk&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=1a1c2630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2MqWHTk</a>)<br />\nHCMP 26/2015 （元朗八鄉橫台山）(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2MrRiLv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MrRiLv&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=5f5c4c42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2MrRiLv</a>)<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n地政總署<br />\n<br />\n一個香港市民<br />\n日期：2019年8月29日"},{"pid":"11eb5fb6599054c9e46b1e7fa29299f4f435a91c","tid":1514951,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTykUks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTykUks.jpg&h=e262c427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3J6Zqr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3J6Zqr9.jpg&h=398279dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFi3Tp